        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>比较简单的练习，不过也花了很久时间。场景布置里的灯光感觉比较玄乎。颜色材质还有一些小内容改了改，没有完全按照教程来。</p></blockquote><p><img src="/image/%E7%A7%AF%E6%9C%A8.png" alt="图片"></p><div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=113181548610906&page=quality:high" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;"></iframe></div><hr><p>快捷键</p><hr><p>m键 合并<br>ctrl+alt+ 0 当前视图添加摄像机<br>alt+ h 全部显示</p>]]></content>
      
      
